detaileddescription.para: This templated, primary constructor creates a new poly mesh writer. The first argument is any Abc (or AbcCoreAbstract) object which can intrusively be converted to an CompoundPropertyWriterPtr to use as a parent, from which the error handler policy for inheritance is also derived. The remaining optional arguments can be used to override the ErrorHandlerPolicy, to specify MetaData, and to set TimeSamplingType.
